                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16206430" author="tilman" created="Mon, 16 Oct 2017 19:16:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The fonts that are rendered invisibly have the &quot;symbolic&quot; flag set in the font descriptor although they are not.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16207757" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 17 Oct 2017 15:14:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1812415 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1812415&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1812415&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3965&quot; title=&quot;Truetype Font glyphs not rendered&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3965&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3965&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: add fallback for bogus &quot;symbol&quot; fonts&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16207758" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 17 Oct 2017 15:14:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1812416 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1812416&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1812416&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3965&quot; title=&quot;Truetype Font glyphs not rendered&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3965&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3965&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: add fallback for bogus &quot;symbol&quot; fonts&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16207763" author="tilman" created="Tue, 17 Oct 2017 15:17:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I initially tried changing &lt;tt&gt;PDSimpleFont.isFontSymbolic()&lt;/tt&gt; but that resulted in regressions. This solution uses a part of the &lt;tt&gt;!isSymbolic()&lt;/tt&gt; branch in codeToGID instead.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
